The Bengal cat draws attention with its unusual, wild-looking coat, reminiscent of leopards.

#### Appearance and Behavior:

- **Coat**: Spotted or marbled, very striking.
- **Activity Level**: High energy, needs a lot of play and exercise.

Learn more about Bengal cats' breeding and behavior at [Bengal House](https://bengalhouse.com/).
